---
// Hero — landing block with headline + featured note card.
// Headline and meta strip are static; edit copy here.
---

<header class="hero">
  <div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow">The door is open · Begin where you are</span>
    </div>

    <h1>
      A new you.<br />
      The unexamined life,<br />
      <span class="ital">examined.</span> Together.
    </h1>

    <p class="lead">
      A slow, deliberate practice for people in transition, building
      a life that fits the shape of who you are becoming, not who you
      were told to be.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/check-in">
        Get Your Free Personalized Assessment
        <span class="btn-arrow" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#story">Read my story</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <aside class="hero-card" aria-label="Featured note">
    <div class="index">
      <span>On Light</span>
      <span>14th C.</span>
    </div>
    <p class="quote">
      "I wish I could show you, when you are lonely or in darkness, the astonishing light of your own being."
    </p>
    <div class="attrib">
      <span class="line" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span>Hafiz</span>
    </div>
    <div class="wax-seal" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/assets/wax-seal.png" alt="" />
    </div>
  </aside>
</header>
